  "description_snippet": "## SUMMARY\n\nSimilar to issue 370856871, on Windows a compromised renderer can call `StartDragging()` to control the mouse and perform clicks. The existing mitigations can be bypassed after a single user tap until browser shutdown, allowing for many of the same impacts as the referenced issue. After"
